## Steps

1. Read `feature_list.json` — identify the next `pending` task
2. Read relevant `.cs` source files for context
3. Write failing xUnit tests
4. Implement the feature
5. Run `dotnet test --filter "{{TEST_FILTER}}"` — confirm green
6. Run `dotnet build` — confirm zero warnings
7. Update `feature_list.json` status to `completed`
8. Append to `claude-progress.txt`
9. Commit changes
